Class AeTaminoConfig

          org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.tamino.AeTaminoConfig
public class AeTaminoConfig
extends AeXMLDBConfig

This class encapsulates the Tamino XQuery statements used by the Active BPEL Tamino based persistence layer. This class uses a SAX parser to first parse an xml file that contains the XQuery queries.

protected java.util.List getStatementConfigFilenames()
